English.Text: You master crafter conducts every crew member as a perfectly synchronised orchestra. "Just any charcoal won't do, it needs to burn at a very high temperature and we don't have much time!" An airtight clay oven is set up and smoking in the blink of an eye. Not an hour has passed before the powdered charred coconut shells are being fed to the agonising officer, cleansing his body from every toxin.
